quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,Asizange yini sikunwebele (sikuvulele) isifuba sakho na
  94,2,Futhi sawususa kuwena umthwalo wakho
  94,3,Lowo owehlisela phansi umhlane wakho
  94,4,Futhi sakunyusela udumo lwakho
  94,5,"Manjalo, ngempela kanye nobunzima kunobulula"
  94,6,Futhi ngempela kanye nobunzima kunobulula
  94,7,Ngakho-ke uma usuqedile (umsebenzi wakho) sukuma (uphinde uthandaze)
  94,8,Futhi fisa eNkosini yakho